==Description==

The [[Image:Sketcher_Create3PointCircle.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_Create3PointCircle|Sketcher Create 3PointCircle]] tool creates a circle from three points along the circle. {{Version|1.0}}: This is the same tool as [[Sketcher_CreateCircle|Sketcher CreateCircle]] but with a different initial mode.

==Usage==

See also: [[Sketcher_Workbench#Drawing_aids|Drawing aids]].

# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Sketcher_Create3PointCircle.svg|16px]] [[Sketcher_Create3PointCircle|Circle From 3 Points]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Sketch → Geometries → [[Image:Sketcher_Create3PointCircle.svg|16px]] Circle From 3 Points}} option from the menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|G}} then {{KEY|3}}, then {{KEY|C}}.
# For further steps see [[Sketcher_CreateCircle#Usage|Sketcher CreateCircle]].


